ygData.messageBody:
I will do any preparations for the Rallos Zek Gnomestock... its too bad that
fireworks are so lame or they'd be a great addition to this event. I have a
reasonable supply of money so funding the booze should be no problem. I've
never coordinated an event like this however, and I am looking forward to
the bertoxxulous event so I can see what works and what doesnt.

Cogg
Rallos Zek
